# Clawkie-Talkie client env template.
#
# Copy to `client/.env.local` and edit. Vite loads these at dev/build
# time; only variables prefixed `VITE_` are exposed to browser code.

# Optional fallback rendezvous URL. Normally unneeded: the daemon bakes
# the rendezvous it registered with into the printed join URL as a
# `rendezvous=` query param, and the client uses that directly when
# present. This env var only applies if someone opens the app without
# a join URL that carries its own rendezvous.
#
# When set, point at the same rendezvous your daemon registers with
# (see daemon/README.md — the daemon's `--rendezvous-url` flag).
#VITE_CT_RENDEZVOUS_URL=http://localhost:8787
